      '[KBC]': '{byang chub sems dpa\'i spyod pa la \'jug pa\'i tshig \'grel \'jam dbyangs bla ma\'i zhal lung bdud rtsi\'i thig pa} \'A word by word commentary on the Bodhisatvacaryāvatāra called Drops of Nectar According to the Personal Statements of the Mañjughoṣha-like Teacher\'. A famous commentary on the Bodhisatvacaryāvatāra by Khenpo Kunphel (1872-1943). Published in Western book form by the Mi Khron Mi Rigs publishing house, 1990, ISBN 7-5409-0405-4/B, 14.',
