      '[LNN]': '{rdzogs pa chen po klong chen snying thig gi sngon \'gro\'i ngag \'don khrigs su bsdebs pa rnam mkhyen lam bzang zhes bya ba bzhugs so//} \'Liturgical arrangement made for the Preliminary Practices of the Longchen Nyingthig Great Completion\', an arrangement made by Jigmey Thrinley Ozer from the teachings of Jigmey Lingpa. Translated by Tony Duff.',
      '[LOM]': '{seng ge\'i gdong can ma\'i sgrub thabs nyung \'dus bdud las rgyal ba\'i bzhad sgra zhes bya ba bzhugs /} A Brief sadhana of Siṃhamukha, \'The Sounds of Laughter Victorious Over Māra\'. A text from the tradition of the Golden Dharmas of Glorious Sakya.',
